quran[15]{c,v,t}:
  91,1,"lbut ko Alongan a go so Sin­dao niyan,"
  91,2,"Go so Olan igira-a tiyondog iyan,"
  91,3,"Go so daondao igira-a piyayag iyan,"
  91,4,"Go so gagawi-i igira-a ipukho­lob iyan,"
  91,5,"Go so Langit, a go so Mimba­lai Ron,"
  91,6,"Go so Lopa a go so Ko­miyayaton,"
  91,7,"Go so ginawa , a go so Mithaongon Phiyapiya:"
  91,8,"Na ini-ilaham Iyan non so Kapumbaradosa niyan, a go so Ka­phangongonotan niyan;-"
  91,9,"Sabunar a miyakada-ag so tao a Siyoti niyan a ginawa niyan;"
  91,10,"Go Sabunar a kiyawiswisan so tao a diyadag iyan a ginawa niyan!"
  91,11,"Piyakambokhag o (Pagtao a) Samood (so Sogo kiran) sabap ko Kiyapangakowala iran;"
  91,12,"Gowani a mbakorot so lubi a darowaka kiran,"
  91,13,"Na Pitharo kiran o Sogo o Allah: (Botawani niyo) so Onta o Allah, go so kaphaginom iyan!"
  91,14,"Na Piyakambokhag iran Su­kaniyan, na biyono iran noto, na bininasa siran o Kadnan Niran sa­bap ko dosa iran, na Piyakapurar­ampata Iyan siran,"
  91,15,"Go di Niyan ikhaluk so kiya­ bolosan noto."
